            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Calidius Eroticus <lb n="2"/>sibi et Fanniae Voluptati <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>ivus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ecit</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>copo <note>sic</note> computemus habes vini |(sextarium) I <expan><abbr>pani</abbr><ex>s</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>sse</ex></expan> I <expan><abbr>pulmentar</abbr><ex>ium</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>ssibus</ex></expan> II convenit <expan><abbr>puell</abbr><ex>a</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>ssibus</ex></expan> VIII et hoc convenit faenum <lb n="6"/>mulo <expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>ssibus</ex></expan> II iste mulus me ad factum <lb n="7"/>dabit
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>(A): Falsche Maßangabe des Inschriftfeldes. (B): Z. 3: CIL: pane statt pani(s). (C): Flobert, AE: wohl 1. Jh.; CIL: puella statt caupo im Dekor. Dialog zwischen einem Reisenden und dem Schankwirt. Material: ockerfarbener Kalkstein.</p>
            </div>
